    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine domini Dei omnipotentis eterni. <persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/21">Berengarius</persName> divina ordinante clemencia <rs
                            key="#Emperor/king">rex</rs>. Si benivola humanitatis gracia regalis
                        benignitas sanctis ac venerabilibus locis temporalia commoda serena mente
                        offerre ac confirmare contendit, profecto eterne retribucionis merito et
                        instantis regiminis soliditate redimita florescet. Omnium igitur sancte Dei
                        Ecclesie nostrorumque fidelium presencium ac futurorum industrie
                        innotescimus, <persName key="#Bishops"><name ref="Salomon"
                            >Salomonem</name></persName> reverendissimum <rs key="#Bishops"
                            >episcopum</rs>, cuius cure ac providencie <orgName
                            key="#Houses #Rivers #Mountains #Curtes #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Mills #Wine #Hay/fodder #Public_exactions #Profits_of_justice #Teloneum #Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium #Churches #Monasteries #Royal_slave #Royal_aldius"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/190"><placeName ref="#places/502">Sancti
                                Galli</placeName></orgName>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">cenobium</rs> commissum perpenditur, <rs
                            key="#Intercessory">interventu</rs>
                        <persName key="#Intercessory #Palatine_count #fidelisOf" ref="#people/57"
                            >Sigisfredi</persName> illustris <rs key="#Palatine_count">sacri palacii
                            nostri comitis</rs> dilectissimi <rs key="#fidelisOf">fidelis</rs>
                        nostri summissis precibus nostram exorasse clemenciam, ut <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Monasteries"
                            >abbaciam nostram</rs> que <orgName
                            key="#Houses #Rivers #Mountains #Curtes #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Mills #Wine #Hay/fodder #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Public_exactions #Profits_of_justice #Teloneum #Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium #Churches #Monasteries #Royal_slave #Royal_aldius"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/191"><placeName
                                key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Monasteries"
                                ref="#places/503">Massini</placeName> nominatur</orgName>, cuius
                        ecclesia in honore sancte Dei genitricis semperque virginis Marie dicata
                        consistit, sita infra regnum nostrum in <rs key="#Comitatus">comitatu</rs>
                        <geogName key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/111">Stacionensi</geogName>, per
                        nostri precepti inscriptionem Beati Galli cenobio in integrum perpetualiter
                        habendum concederemus. Quorum obsecracionem benigne suscipientes, ratam
                        atque omnino recipiendam laudantes, divini cultus sanctorum ardore succensi,
                        ut sua nos <rs key="#Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium">tuicione</rs> defendat et
                        eterne vite salutem acquirat, quidquid ubique exinde infra nostri regni
                        fines pertinere dinoscitur beatissimi confessoris Cristi Galli monasterio,
                        in quo corporis eius sanctissima gleba quiescit, iam fatam abbaciam Massini
                        dictam per hoc nostre dapsilitatis pragmaticon cum <rs key="#Curtes"
                            >curtibus</rs>, <rs key="#Churches">cappellis ac oratoris</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Houses">casis</rs> ac ceteris omnibus, <rs key="#Wine"
                        >vineis</rs>, <rs key="#Hay/fodder">pratis</rs>, <rs key="#Hay/fodder"
                            >pascuis</rs>, <rs key="#Forests">silvis</rs>, <rs>salectis</rs>,
                            <rs>saccionibus</rs>, <rs key="#Rivers">aquis aquarumque
                        decursibus</rs>, <rs key="#Mills">molendinis</rs>, <rs key="#Fisheries"
                            >piscacionibus</rs>, <rs key="#Teloneum">theloneis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Public_exactions">reddicionibus</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Profits_of_justice">districtionibus</rs>, <rs key="#Mountains"
                            >montibus</rs>, <rs key="#Natural_landscape">vallibus, planiciebus</rs>,
                            <rs key="#Landed_possessions">cultis et incultis , divisis et non
                            divisis</rs>, <rs key="#Royal_slave">servis et ancillis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Royal_aldius">aldionibus et aldianis</rs> ac <rs
                            key="#Royal_slave">familiis utriusque sexus</rs> seu cum omnibus que
                        dici vel nominari possunt ad eandem abbaciam pertinentibus atque
                        aspicientibus, adiacentibus atque longinquis absque minoracione aliqua vel
                        refregacione offerimus, largimur et confirmamus habendum et inconvulse in
                        perpetuum possidendum, excepta molestia cuiuscumque. Si quis igitur hoc
                        nostre offersionis et confirmacionis preceptum aliquando in aliquo
                        infringere temptaverit aut aliqua a predicto Beati Galli cenobio subtrahere
                        quesierit, ut conatus eius instabilis sit, noverit se compositurum <rs
                            key="#Penalty">auri obriti libras centum</rs>, <rs key="#Camera_regis"
                            >medietatem camere palacii nostri</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Camera_of_other_public_authorities">medietatem prelibato Sancti
                            Galli cenobio</rs>. Quod ut verius credatur et diligencius ab omnibus
                        observetur, manu propria roboratum annuli nostri inpressione subter
                        assignari precepimus. Signum domni Berengarii excellentissimi regis.
                            <persName key="#Chancellor"><name ref="Ambrosius"
                            >Ambrosius</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Chancellor">cancellarius</rs> ad vicem [<persName
                            key="#Archchancellor #Bishops" ref="#people/216">Ardingi</persName>] <rs
                            key="#Bishops">episcopi</rs> et <rs key="#Archchancellor"
                            >archicancellarii</rs> recognovi [et subscripsi]. Data kal. Iunii, anno
                        dominice incarnacionis DCCCCIIII, domni vero Berengarii regis XXIII,
                        indictione VII. Actum <placeName ref="#places/65">palacio
                            Ticinensi</placeName>. In Cristi nomine feliciter, amen.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
